   411→    }
   412→  }
   413→
   414→  /**
   415→   * Get the timestamp of the most recent email in database
   416→   *
   417→   * Used for incremental fetching - only fetch emails newer than this timestamp.
   418→   *
   419→   * @returns Most recent email timestamp, or null if no emails exist
